### List products (paged)
GET http://localhost:8080/products?page=0&size=20

### Search similar products
GET http://localhost:8080/products/search?query=headphones&k=5

### Search for kitchen items
GET http://localhost:8080/products/search?query=cooking&k=5

### Search for sports gear
GET http://localhost:8080/products/search?query=running shoes&k=5

### Add one random product
POST http://localhost:8080/products/add

### Add 10 random products
POST http://localhost:8080/products/add?count=10
